                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          target="_blank" aria-label="Navigate to the Microsoft documentation for Standard date and time format strings">standard</a> &
            <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/standard/base-types/custom-date-and-time-format-strings" target="_blank" aria-label="Navigate to the Microsoft documentation for custom date and time format strings"> custom date and time format strings</a>        as specified in MSDN.
